cc:Work.dc:title: landscape w/ birds
cc:Work.dc:description: Birds are clones of two 3-part polybezier curves. Landscape is a mix of noise filled rectangles, with straight line fractalized, filled and noisy blured in foreground. Neither is very good by itself, but the two together are not all that bad. The bezier curve birds can be pretty versitile.
